	* mini-x86.h, mini-x86.c, exceptions-x86.c: Align stack on all
	platforms, with definable stack alignment value.  Set to 16 now
	for all platforms.

	* mini.c, mini.h, driver.c: Command line option for disabling
	stack alignment.

