	* mini-amd64.c (mono_arch_local_regalloc): Fix some regalloc problems
	with global registers.
	(mono_arch_output_basic_block): Fix SWITCH in the AOT case.

	* aot.c (emit_method_code): Fix the 'method emitted as' messages.

