	mono_debugger_handle_exception() to tell the debugger about
	catch/finally clauses.

2004-10-18  Zoltan Varga  <vargaz@freemail.hu>

	* exceptions-amd64.c (mono_arch_find_jit_info): Pop arguments of the stack.

